Every week a Guardian Money reader submits a question, and it’s up to you to help him or her out – a selection of the best answers will appear in next Saturday’s paper. We have always fancied a hot tub, but never had the money. However, we noticed that Aldi was selling an inflatable one for £350. Do the cheap ones do the job, and do they last? I don’t want to throw my money down the drain. Do you have a problem readers could solve? Email your suggestions to money@theguardian.com or write to us at Money, the Guardian, Kings Place, 90 York Way, London N1 9GU.